      "raw_text": "The Columbia Sash, Door & Lum-\nDer company will start its new\nplant, located at the crossing Of\nthe Spokane Falls & Northern and\nMorton street, next week. The main\nbuilding of this new concern is\nS0x100 feet and the entire plant is\nthoroughly up to date in every re-\nspect being supplied with the most\nimproved machinery. The officers\nof the company are: d. Delain,\npresident and John Munich, secre-\ntary. The company is incorporated\nfor 100000. Already orders are\ncoming in from all parts of the\ncountry, and the company would\nseem to have a bright future in\nsight."
